item.title: CVE-2023-0071|2024-08-02T04:54:32.615Z -- unknown -- wp%20tabs
item.description: The WP Tabs WordPress plugin before 2.1.17 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
